Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,things\Nprior to anyization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the collective karma. You have\Nthe collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that we cleared this morning\Nhad to do with something coming out of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective unconscious.\NYou have the karma of mankind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own individual karma.\NUm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what appears to be a problem or a bad\Nhabit or or a negative at one point
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,later on is not seen to be that way.\NIt was only the way you were holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, it isn't a reality of\Na thing, but your perception and your
