Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.08,0:24:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,can't trust breathing anymore. Food's\Nall full of poisons. All the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,corporations are corrupt. The church is\Nfalling down with pedophilia and god
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.67,0:24:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,knows what.\NEverything is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.55,0:24:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a body is a problem. Breathing in\Nand out is a problem. Money is a
