Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:24:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The past and the future are both\Nproblems. And the present is a really
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.48,0:25:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,big problem.\NSo this is all how you conceptualize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.67,0:25:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go back 10 years ago, go back 10\Nyears ago. Now think ahead to this
