Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is it a problem how can it be a problem\Nif It has no relevance to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.91,0:26:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of the whole problem of\Nproblems.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.48,0:26:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A problem is whatever you think a\Nproblem is. You know what I'm saying? Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if surrendering your life to God is\Nsomething that you understand the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,essence of the divinity of it, then it's\Na sacrament.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.91,0:26:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The sacrifice of the animal is its\Nsacrament to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's its form of\Nexpressing its value to all of life. The
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.44,0:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,same with bad habits or neurosis.\NAnyway, these are all perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is\Nwhat a person does traditionally in
