Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.36,0:28:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be provided.\NSo, a bad habit then would depend on how
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.39,0:28:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you define it, where you are in your\Nlevel of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.32,0:28:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um\Nand neurosis are really psychological
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.55,0:28:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,problems and all all of these things\Ncome up all of these things come up and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of consciousness\Nalmost everyone in its audience has
