Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.84,0:29:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as very advanced teachers, it\Nsays, um, that's a hard one to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.52,0:29:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Nthe core of that which you are is
