Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.64,0:29:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,some degree of persona resumes.\NOh, the jocular repartee which this uh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.60,0:29:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,persona is prone to you know it does it\Nof its own. It's that's what persists
