Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere. You don't hear anything.\NThere's nothing to read or there's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.15,0:30:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to know. So, there's no pursuit\Nof knowledge. You see, and because of
