Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.80,0:38:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um\None gives it uh you might say sufficient
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,energy to\Nenable the continuence of a human
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.35,0:38:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime especially to reenter the world\Nto continue. But that's arbitrary. One
