Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.32,0:39:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to a functioning.\NThis has also its karmic u commitments
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.28,0:39:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,uh that may bring it about. We see some\Nwhat happened to some people. We see
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that Romanoi for instance suddenly fell\Ndown as a teenager and thought he was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.64,0:39:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,dying and u\Nu was pretty much left for dead. I think
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.83,0:39:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the bugs were eating him up and he was\Nuh dehydrated and stopped eating and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:40:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,um\Nso it takes time. He was silent, didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.20,0:40:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,speak for two years. So it takes time to\Nlike re-energize
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.28,0:40:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's usually because of the it's\Nbecause of well not usually it's always
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.04,0:40:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the input of people around\Nyou to eat and um breathe and sleep and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,do all those things and the love of such\Npeople uh then begins to get the bug to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.32,0:40:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,stir again like it's coming out of\Nits winter hibernation. So the
