Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.16,0:40:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,be revived through the energy input.\NUm
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect on uh our family of our own\Nspiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.20,0:40:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,um\Neffort then is um both good and bad. On
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.07,0:40:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the one hand it may energize them.\NWe certainly can set examples at certain
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.76,0:41:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,levels that we can actually that we can\Nimplement. I think crossing over 200 is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.35,0:41:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,something where the the spiritual seeker\Nin the family does have an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.59,0:41:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um to insist on integrity, to insist on\Nthe demonstration of integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.28,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,uh is one where external pressure does\Nhave an effect and that is at a place
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where I'm\Nchief of staff. Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.44,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the rehabilitation of of these children\Nhas to do with trying to get them to the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.92,0:41:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,level of integrity to admit that I am\Nresponsible for my own action.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.28,0:41:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't get above integrity\Nuntil you say yes, I'm the one that did
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.59,0:41:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that. So long as you're blaming gimbals\Nfor falling on the ice on the sidewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.31,0:41:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still below 200 because gimbals\Ndidn't push you over on the ice, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.56,0:41:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was your how you put your feet.\NYou saw it was icy. You're 52 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.68,0:42:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you know how to put your feet on\Nice, you shouldn't be walking on the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.72,0:42:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of gimbals and much less suing\Ngimbble. So, I mean, I've never had much
